  <body>
    <header><para styleclass="Heading1">Configuring</para></header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text style="font-weight:bold;">Configuration precedence (lowest to highest):</text> compiled-in struct defaults &lt; <text styleclass="Code Example">EmulatrV4.ini</text> &lt; command-line qualifiers. The committed ini drives a no-flag launch; a CLI qualifier overrides the ini for a single run. <text styleclass="Code Example">IniLoader</text> populates <text styleclass="Code Example">EmulatorSettings</text>, which is the single source of truth threaded to every consumer.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading2">Settings</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="7" colcount="5" style="border-width:0px; border-spacing:0px; border-collapse:collapse; cell-border-width:1px; border-color:#000000; border-style:solid; head-row-background-color:#00ffff; alt-row-background-color:none;">
      <thead style="vertical-align:top">
        <td><para styleclass="Normal"><text style="font-weight:bold;">Field</text></para></td>
